The paper deals with video deblurring, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of stereo video and 3D scene flow also suggests that the paper could be categorized under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of iterative weighting schemes, which is a common technique in robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.AI).
